   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1904_AS_RBH_1_00016"/>Dr Richard Beer-Hofmann</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb173" type="place">Rodaun</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb40101" type="place">Liesingerstraße</rs></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1904_AS_RBH_1_00018"/><date when="1904-06-02">2. 6. 904</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>lieber Richard,</salute> wie wär es, we<c rendition="#gemination-n"/> man<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ich wieder einmal<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ähe? – Z. B. <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01404-1"/><date>Montag</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01404-1"><ref target="1904-06-06" subtype="See" type="schnitzler-tagebuch"/>.
               </note><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>Abend</time> in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb63">Hietzing</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb304"><hi rend="latintype">Kuffner</hi></rs>?</p><p>– <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10815">Bahr</rs> möchte <hi rend="latintype">ev.</hi>
               auch hinkommen. An welchen Vormittagen pflegen Sie in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb173">Rodaun</rs> zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein?</p><closer>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
